{"tid":2052504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【政情】國安法諮詢「建制限定」 是否上書民主派各自爬山","createTime":"2020-06-05T14:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T15:15:35.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9135aa46cf00a66d395cdd7ea49764e81390499a","tid":2052504,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:43:35.000Z","msg":"【政情】國安法諮詢「建制限定」 是否上書民主派各自爬山<br />\n47分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n<code>節錄</code><br />\n港區國安法無公開諮詢，徵詢名單亦無提及民主派 ... ...<br />\n<br />\n有民主派指，諮詢名單嚴重偏聽，他們討論過應否正式提交意見，包括... ... <br />\n<br />\n不過有<span style=\"color: gold;\">資深民主派</span>認為，整條國安法的立法程序完全毋須經過香港立法會，加上中央處事向來寧左勿右，應在法例成事前，透過<span style=\"color: gold;\">傳話人</span>向北京進言，... ...<br />\n<br />\n民主派在行動上和勇不分，但是否向北京進言，一派拒絕與狼共舞，另一派仍期望<span style=\"color: gold;\">減低陣痛</span>。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393460&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=2ac8bd20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393460&h=c1f7e04b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393460</a>"},{"pid":"40b9c25893f88ae91c2669352669367d1a037f7d","tid":2052504,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"Thanos 演員repost香港64晚會被禁既ig story<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2052493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2052493</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b594ed504c77e4d4fb720dc9d17883a2869c0fb0","tid":2052504,"uid":37957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"民主黨my香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b2b98f57e87dcb6e1ec37b8e6de83b44237117","tid":2052504,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:50:35